data.description: Beautiful 6 Bedroom 5 bath home with 3 car garage in the community of Sun N Lakes golf club. This home features spacious rooms and tons of space. Downstairs You have huge formal dining area. Also you have a spacious kitchen and living area. Upstairs you have a nice den area and 5 more bedrooms including a large primary bedroom with 2 walk in closets, shower and garden tub with dual vanities. This home has 2 HVAC systems for heating and cooling also the roof was redone in 2022. This home is located in sun n lakes community which offers amenities such as golf,resturaunt, community center, pool and tennis. This home has been well maintained and is move in ready don’t miss out on this one schedule your private showing today!
